ygData.messageBody:
Hi!

I'm a level 10 High Elf Enchantress on Luclin server. You can find me
running around BB or GFay in my purple robe and my ear cleanerlike
staff. I can't wait to get to level 12 so I can get some new spells
and really start exploring.

I love playing EQ, I'm in no way addicted because there's little time
to play outside of work and school. My fiance also plays too, which
limits my time too :P

I just wanted to say hi! This looks like a really cool group to be in!
